                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970531-15-off75 t17970531-15-cd76"></join>, one looking-glass with a gilt frame, value 8s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17970531-15-victim192" type="victimName">
